                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "CYCLING IS NOT JUST ABOUT THE BIKE. IT'S ABOUT THE JOURNEY, THE PEOPLE, AND THE RELENTLESS WILL TO KEEP PEDALING.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.1,
